title: 668 - Skywriter | Trending Tuesday
description:
Painting with clouds is never easy, so its the perfect time for Scooter to get on the CB and get to the bottom of why the sky is not full of more writing. (story at about 17 minutes if you skip the intro please support the podcast via patreon or one of our sponsors)

You can find all of our sponsors or become a patron on our new website www.sleepwithmepodcast.com

Go getters who go get goats!
